video.title: In the Dark
video.synopsis: A blind woman with vices finds herself in the middle of a murder investigation when her best friend turns up dead.

episodes.synopsis: When Murphy, a hard-drinking blind woman, discovers her friend's dead body, she realizes she’s the only one willing to find the killer.
episodes.title: Pilot

episodes.synopsis: Murphy goes on a date in exchange for information. Jess tries to spice up her relationship. Chloe sets her father up with an unlikely lover.
episodes.title: Mommy Issues

episodes.synopsis: Murphy organizes a school assembly to track down a student with a secret. Max gets injured during sex, while Murphy denies her feelings for him.
episodes.title: The Big Break

episodes.synopsis: Murphy and Max test the limits of their relationship as they hit the road to look for the mysterious woman Tyson cheated on his girlfriend with.
episodes.title: The Graduate

episodes.synopsis: Murphy deals with a pregnancy scare while trying to find a dead body she can touch to put her doubts about misidentifying Tyson’s corpse to rest.
episodes.title: The Feels

episodes.synopsis: When her worst fears are confirmed, Murphy sinks into a spiraling depression. Dean and Jules try to get some answers from Tyson’s father.
episodes.title: Tyson

episodes.synopsis: After identifying a suspect in Tyson's murder, Murphy takes Chloe out to celebrate, not realizing she’s putting both their lives in danger.
episodes.title: The One That Got Away

episodes.synopsis: Murphy attempts to embrace domestic bliss with Max, but news of Tyson’s second killer sends her looking for answers.
episodes.title: Jessica Rabbit

episodes.synopsis: Max makes a choice that could cause trouble for Darnell. Dean sorts through his feelings for Murphy. Jess has a secret that threatens her relationship.
episodes.title: Deal or No Deal

episodes.synopsis: Max and Murphy go on the run. Dean and Jules work hard to crack the Tyson case, even as Jules tries to protect Darnell.
episodes.title: Bait and Switch

episodes.synopsis: Murphy hunts for a missing Max. Jess accuses Murphy of being addicted to Tyson’s case. Felix deals with an audit initiated by his mother.
episodes.title: I Woke Up Like This

episodes.synopsis: Murphy celebrates her birthday with friends and family. Murphy decides to take a break from Tyson’s murder case, but Jules digs deeper by following Nia.
episodes.title: Rollin' with the Homies

episodes.synopsis: Jules looks for a crooked cop. Murphy gives it a shot with Dean, who makes a surprising confession.
episodes.title: It's Always Been You

episodes.synopsis: Murphy is on the mend after a terrifying encounter, but an ominous visit spurs her into action. She devises a plan to stay safe and save Guiding Hope.
episodes.title: It's All About the Benjamin

episodes.synopsis: Murphy gets a surprise visit while the Guiding Hope team tries to cover up the new business venture. Darnell visits Nia and things take an unexpected turn.
episodes.title: Cross My Heart and Hope to Lie

episodes.synopsis: Guiding Hope’s monetary surplus puts them on the radar of the IRS and Felix decides to take matters into his own hands. Dean gathers dirt on Nia.
episodes.title: Son of a Gun

episodes.synopsis: Murphy faces a life-or-death situation, while Dean attempts to address his own problems. Felix struggles to balance his dating life with his dealing life.
episodes.title: Deal Me In

episodes.synopsis: Murphy’s choices entangles the Guiding Hope crew deeper into Nia’s game. Pressure mounts as Darnell fails to deliver and Max is haunted by his former life.
episodes.title: The Unusual Suspects

episodes.synopsis: Murphy and Felix juggle extracurricular activities with the demands of dealing, and Jess is targeted by Nia. Dean has to deal with Chloe’s rebelliousness.
episodes.title: The Truth Hurts

episodes.synopsis: Max's luck continues to spiral, forcing Murphy to take extreme risks. Felix contends with issues at Guiding Hope and Jess's relationships are tested.
episodes.title: The Straw That Broke the Camel's Back

episodes.synopsis: Murphy convinces Jess to help with a drug mission, while Felix finds himself in a legal predicament. Dean’s partner shows real talent on the job.
episodes.title: Codependence Day

episodes.synopsis: When Murphy and Felix concoct a new plan to destroy Nia, Murphy’s friendship with Josh pays off. Jess makes a bold move with Sterling.
episodes.title: How to Succeed in Business Without Really Dying

episodes.synopsis: Murphy and Felix swing for the fences with plan to end their arrangement with Nia. Dean tries to escape his increasingly dire circumstances.
episodes.title: The Last Dance

episodes.synopsis: The stakes are high as the crew contends with the fallout of their attempt to cut off Nia’s supply and take her down.
episodes.title: Bad People

episodes.synopsis: With Nia’s shipment missing and the Guiding Hope crew pressured to deliver it, Murphy, Jess, Felix and Max will stop at nothing to find the stash.
episodes.title: Where Have You Ben?

episodes.synopsis: A betrayal leads to dire consequences, and the fallout causes devastating outcomes for Murphy and the Guiding Hope team.
episodes.title: My Pride and Joy

episodes.synopsis: With Nia dead and Josh aware of their involvement in the case, Murphy, Jess, Felix and Max head back to a familiar place. Josh and Clemens dig deeper.
episodes.title: Hanging by a Thread

episodes.synopsis: Murphy, Jess, Felix and Max begin a long and arduous journey as they attempt to stay one step ahead of Josh and Clemens.
episodes.title: I Know What You Did Last Night

episodes.synopsis: Murphy experiences being truly alone in an unfamiliar place and begins to feel helpless — until she meets a kind stranger willing to go on a road trip.
episodes.title: Somewhere Over the Border

episodes.synopsis: When $300,000 of his money goes missing, Josiah enlists Darnell to track down Murphy. Later, Murphy and Trey try to pull off a heist to get the funds.
episodes.title: Safe and Sound

episodes.synopsis: Murphy reaches out to an unlikely source for help in getting to Jess, while Trey hatches a plan of his own.
episodes.title: Planes, Trains and Automobiles

episodes.synopsis: Murphy's desperate attempt to save Jess lands her in a tough position. A disagreement between Clemens and Josh has serious consequences.
episodes.title: Arcade Fire

episodes.synopsis: Murphy, Felix and Max look to Josiah for answers about Jess' whereabouts. Clemens' bold move pays off.
episodes.title: Pretty in Pink

episodes.synopsis: Tensions run high when Murphy, Felix, Max, Lesley and Trey decide to ride out a snowstorm together during a power outage.
episodes.title: Power Trip

episodes.synopsis: When Murphy starts to spin out, Felix steps in. But their mission soon pushes Felix to a breaking point.
episodes.title: Excess Baggage

episodes.synopsis: Murphy follows another lead while fending for herself as Clemens and Josh continue their hunt for Murphy.
episodes.title: Home Run

episodes.synopsis: Still determined to solve the Jennifer Walker case, Murphy takes advantage of an opportunity that comes knocking on Darnell's door.
episodes.title: Match Point

episodes.synopsis: Murphy's search for Jess uncovers new details about Jenny. Felix lands in the interrogation room, and Clemens and Josh inch closer to finding Murphy.
episodes.title: Do You Hear What I Hear?

episodes.synopsis: The truth about Jess is revealed, and Murphy is forced to take a closer look at the person she has become.
episodes.title: Expectation Is the Root of All Heartache
